eady-for-dev → in-progress\n   200→        </output>\n   201→      </check>\n   202→\n   203→      <check if=\"current status == 'in-progress'\">\n   204→        <output>⏯️ Resuming work on story {{story_key}}\n   205→          Story is already marked in-progress\n   206→        </output>\n   207→      </check>\n   208→\n   209→      <check if=\"current status is neither ready-for-dev nor in-progress\">\n   210→        <output>⚠️ Unexpected story status: {{current_status}}\n   211→          Expected ready-for-dev or in-progress. Continuing anyway...\n   212→        </output>\n   213→      </check>\n   214→\n   215→      <action>Store {{current_sprint_status}} for later use</action>\n   216→    </check>\n   217→\n   218→    <check if=\"{{sprint_status}} file does NOT exist\">\n   219→      <output>ℹ️ No sprint status file exists - story progress will be tracked in story file only</output>\n   220→      <action>Set {{current_sprint_status}} = \"no-sprint-tracking\"</action>\n   221→    </check>\n   222→  </step>\n   223→\n   224→  <step n=\"5\" goal=\"Implement task following red-green-refactor cycle\">\n   225→    <critical>FOLLOW THE STORY FILE TASKS/SUBTASKS SEQUENCE EXACTLY AS WRITTEN - NO DEVIATION</critical>\n   226→\n   227→    <action>Review the current task/subtask from the story file - this is your authoritative implementation guide</action>\n   228→    <action>Plan implementation following red-green-refactor cycle</action>\n   229→\n   230→    <!-- RED PHASE -->\n   231→    <action>Write FAILING tests first for the task/subtask functionality</action>\n   232→    <action>Confirm tests fail before implementation - this validates test correctness</action>\n   233→\n   234→    <!-- GREEN PHASE -->\n   235→    <action>Implement MINIMAL code to make tests pass</action>\n   236→    <action>Run tests to confirm they now pass</action>\n   237→    <action>Handle error conditions and edge cases as specified in task/subtask</action>\n   238→\n   239→    <!-- REFACTOR P